#US #COVID19 #vaccine  Vaccine update for the US for 2/4. States now have had 57.5MM doses shipped to them , with the current US average at 64% of them into peoples arms. ND/WV/NM/SD remain at the top. 

AL/KS/ID/MA remain at the bottom. #NJ slips to 38th in the US in % Used. https://t.co/5rJFpZ1e3B
